messages.content:
Salaam 

Hope you are well 

My name is Sameer I am Team Leader at Human Appeal based in Glasgow. We have our Comedy Takeover Show coming to Glasgow on the 15th Dec 23. Reaching out to see if you could support, we are raising funds for our Winter Gaza Emergency. 

Night of family entertainment Ali Official, Aatif Nawaz, Tez Ilyas, Azeem Muhammed, and Riaad Moosa.
 
Gather your friends and family and book your tickets now:

https://humanappeal.org.uk/events/2023/the-comedy-takeover

We can offer you some complimentary tickets if you would share this whenever you can or 2 times a week. 
Just tag me or @humanappeal on insta.
